<body>
    <h2 class="heading  ">To the most beautiful I know in this world..</h2>

    <section class="sec">
        <div id="first-phrase">
            <p>Every night, I stay up so i can watch you sleep,</p>
            <p>Watching your beauty, it almost makes me weep,</p>
            <p>How I cherish the little dances you do in our call,</p>
            <p>I look at you, and your cutenes</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec">
        <div id="second-phrase">
            <p>Remember the day you confessed,</p>
            <p>I think back to those time and I cant help but wonder, boy arent I blessed</p>
            <p>Ever since that day, a distance of 2000km 1600km between us</p>
            <p>That is until Jan 18, in that Subway, where our hands held.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec">
        <div id="third-phrase">
            <p>I remember us under that starry night sky,</p>
            <p>At the side of those long green grasses, standing on the crooked road,</p>
            <p>I remember me getting lost in your eyes,</p>
            <p>As we shared a kiss, your lower lip pressed between mine.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec">
        <div id="fouth-phrase">
            <p>I think of you everyday,</p>
            <p>I see someone I wish to share my morning and night,</p>
            <p>Someone I want to hug and hold so tight,</p>
            <p>And I open my eyes, there stands you.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec">
        <div id="fifth-phrase">
            <p>You with the brightest smile in the whole wide world</p>
            <p>A smile so bright it blinds me everytime,</p>
            <p>Yet I cant tear my eyes away from you, even if I tried</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec">
        <div id="sixth-phrase">
            <p>For years to come, I hope we stick like glue</p>
            <p>Together and forever, just me and you</p>
            <p>As you will always be my greatest achievement,</p>
            <p>And my greatest reward.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>